readable.content: A dark haired woman wearing a brown jacket and fatigue bottoms and a balding man wearing a green sweater and blue jeans with a fishing pole , stand at the foot of the surf . A man and woman fishing at the beach . A man and a woman are standing on a shore while the man fishes in the choppy water . A man is fishing in the ocean with a large woman walking to the left . Man and woman fishing in the ocean .
